abstract: Intel says that the chips would begin the transformation of today’s stuttering and blurry Web videos into high-resolution quality, full-screen quality.
snippet: Intel says that the chips would begin the transformation of today’s stuttering and blurry Web videos into high-resolution quality, full-screen quality.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO, Nov. 11 — Intel plans to announce a family of microprocessor chips on Monday that it says will speed the availability of high-definition video via the Internet.

headline.main: Intel to Unveil Chips for Improving Video Quality on the Web
headline.print_headline: Intel to Unveil Chips for Improving Video Quality on the Web
